    "Offline-first note-taking with markdown editor",
    "AI chat with multiple provider support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, Ollama)",
    "Database views with table and board layouts",
    "Task management with inbox, today, and upcoming views",
    "Daily notes with automatic creation",
    "Wikilinks and backlinks for note connections",
    "Full-text search and tag filtering",
    "File attachments and previews",
    "SQLite-based indexing for fast search"
